          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "blog_title",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "html",
              "settings": {
                "html": "<div class='section-header'><div class='antor-badge'>ARTICLES</div><h2>Latest Stories & <span class='orange-italic'>Insights</span></h2><p>Sharing thoughts, lessons, and deep-dives on modern web design, typography, and frontend engineering craft.</p></div>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "blog_grid",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "html",
              "settings": {
                "html": "<div class='blog-showcase-grid'><div class='blog-post-card'><div class='img-wrap'><img src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531403009284-440f080d1e12?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80' alt='Design Systems'/><span class='blog-tag'>Design Systems</span></div><div class='blog-body'><div class='blog-meta'><span>June 24, 2026</span><span>•</span><span>5 min read</span></div><h3>The Anatomy of a Modern Minimalist Design System</h3><p>Discover how to build lightweight, scaleable, and highly consistent UI components that empower product design teams to ship fast.</p><div class='blog-footer'><div class='blog-author'><img src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1535713875002-d1d0cf377fde?auto=format&fit=crop&w=150&h=150&q=80' alt='Author'/><div><h4>Antor Roy</h4><p>Lead UI/UX Designer</p></div></div><span class='read-more'>Read →</span></div></div></div><div class='blog-post-card'><div class='img-wrap'><img src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516962215378-7fa2e137ae93?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80' alt='Typography'/><span class='blog-tag'>Typography</span></div><div class='blog-body'><div class='blog-meta'><span>June 18, 2026</span><span>•</span><span>4 min read</span></div><h3>Why Typography is 90% of Your User Experience</h3><p>A deep dive into hierarchy, line-heights, tracking, and the psychology of reading online. Learn how to pair exquisite typefaces.</p><div class='blog-footer'><div class='blog-author'><img src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1535713875002-d1d0cf377fde?auto=format&fit=crop&w=150&h=150&q=80' alt='Author'/><div><h4>Antor Roy</h4><p>Lead UI/UX Designer</p></div></div><span class='read-more'>Read →</span></div></div></div></div>"
